@startuml
title Statechart diagram of the class "Plane"

[*] --> Order
state Order
state Arrival
state Preparation
state Operations
state Maintenance
state OutOfService
state Historic

Order : entry / Plane acquired
Order --> Arrival : plane delivered

Arrival --> Preparation : plane arrived

Preparation --> Operations : plane prepared and ready for operations
Operations --> [*] : plane still has scheduled flights
Operations --> Maintenance : no more scheduled flights or maintenance required

Maintenance --> Preparation : checked and serviced, ready for operations

OutOfService --> [*] : plane is no longer available for use

@enduml
